title: The Buy-­to-­Build Indicator

subtitle: New Estimates for Britain and the United States

author: Joseph A. Francis

abstract: This note presents new long-term estimates of what Jonathan Nitzan and Shimshon Bichler have named the ‘buy-­to-­build indicator’, which is calculated as the value of mergers and acquisitions as a percentage of gross capital formation. 

date: October 2013 

