cite: Joseph A. Francis (2013), ‘The Buy-to-Built Indicator: New Estimates for Britain and the United States’, <i>Review of Capital as Power</i>, Vol. 1, No. 1, pp. 63-72.

keywords: buy-to-build indicator, United States, Britain, mergers and acquisitions, 
